textBox.richText: I just gained the knowledge on how to create one of those lil’ pictures-next-to-the-URL dealies, which explains why there is now one present up there! Now the site’s URL doesn’t look like a fail whereupon it was a “little engine that could” and, try as it might, it could not muster the ability to load its picture thing. Also, if you are ever looking for hilarious shenanigans: play Super Smash Bros’ special brawl with everyone being tiny, have bunny ears, and the game speed be fast; and then have everyone be Ice Climbers and play in Hyrule Temple. The reverse is also equally as funny: all play as Bowser, with the same parameters, on the Battlefield.
